Maharashtra
Dec 16, 2014
Abuse
Description:
			A rickshaw driver was arrested by the Naupada police here for allegedly molesting and stripping a teenage college girl, the city police said here today.

PSI A M Kolekar of the Naupada police station told PTI that the accused Satosh Undru Pandit (31), was called to the girl's house on the fateful night after her family suspected that he abused and defamed her.

When he was asked about why he had abused her, he got annoyed and abused her mother and sister.

After the girl went to rescue them, the accused reportedly used slang and molested her.

As per the police complaint, he also stripped the girl on the street at midnight, 

The accused was arrested within hours at 2.30 am on December 15, the police said.

